    <abstract>
      <t>This document specifies the payload format for packetization of Global System for Mobile Communications Half Rate (GSM-HR) speech codec data into the Real-time Transport Protocol (RTP).  The payload format supports transmission of multiple frames per payload and packet loss robustness methods using redundancy. [STANDARDS-TRACK]</t>
